        <h1>Earth. Fire. Air. Water</h1>
        <h2>Only the Avatar can master all four elements and bring balance to the world.</h2>
         <p>"The Legend of Korra" follows Korra of the southern watertribe, 70 years after the events of "Avatar: the Last Airbender". She leaves the Southern Watertribe after being trained by Katara and begins her journey in Republic City. Her goal is to learn airbending. </p> 
        <p> Unbeknownst to her, the city has need of her as a radical group called the Equalists grows within the city. They seek to equalize the city, uplifting non-benders and eliminating benders.</p>
